- Revisit `st.compile(...)`

# Uploading to Pypi

```bash
# bump version
python -m pip install build twine
python -m build
twine check dist/*
twine upload dist/*
```

# Deploy docs

```bash
flyctl launch
flyctl deploy
flyctl ips list -a stepping-docs
# set A record to @, IPv4
# set AAAA record to @, IPv6
flyctl certs create -a stepping-docs stepping.site

cd docs/doks
npm install
npm run start
npm run build
cd ..; flyctl deploy; cd -

cd docs
python ../scripts/md.py ../ $(find -L ../docs-md -name '**.md')
```
